title: River Road Time Trial/Maryville Downtown Crit
Gran Fondo Sumner County Classic Road Race
NashvilleCyclist.com Coliseum Criterium
description: This criterium will prove to be a fast fun event for all categories.  This race is a TBRA Division I event with a total purse of $3,600!
course: Course is seven tenths of a mile with 8 turns and excellent pavement, a fast,  safe and wide open course!
registration: Registration opens at 7:00 AM & closes 15 minutes prior to each start, All start times Central Standard Time
directions: Downtown Nashville next to Tennessee Titans football stadium.  From I-24W/I-65N take Shelby Ave exit, turn left & then turn right just past Exxon station.  From I-24E/I-65S take James Robertson Pkwy exit, straight then right on Shelby Ave at Exxon station, then next right into stadium area.  The course will be on your right, which is the east side of the stadium.
